text.section:
The return shall show the:
Gross revenues received subject to the tax imposed under KRS 136.616;
Amount billed by the provider for multichannel video programming service subject to the tax imposed under KRS 136.604;
Amount of the tax due under KRS 136.604 and 136.616; and
Any other information as the department deems necessary for the proper administration of KRS 136.600 to 136.660.
